<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Python Packages</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p><ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> uses pip for installing Python packages. When installing <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> software components, pip V8.1.1 is automatically installed. </p>
            <note othertype="note">Check whether pip is already installed on the machine on which the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> components are to be installed. The installation fails if V8.1.2 or a version older than V7.0.3 is already installed.</note>
        </section>
